section.section.small-form.js-fade-in
  .site-container
    .small-form__container
      h2.small-form__heading.site-heading Обсудить проект
      form.small-form(data-need-validation)
        .small-form__form-container
          label.form__label.small-form__label
            input(type="text" name="name" data-parsley-required class="form__input js-input")
            span.form__label-name.js-input-heading Ваше имя
            +error
          label.form__label.small-form__label
            input(type="text" name="name" data-parsley-required class="form__input js-input js-phone-mask")
            span.form__label-name.js-input-heading Номер телефона
            +error
        .small-form__form-container
          .form__btn-wrapper.small-form__label.small-form__btn-wrapper
            +button("Отправить", null, null, null)(class="form__btn")
            label.form__agreement
              input(type="checkbox" data-parsley-required class="visually-hidden")
              span.form__agreement-text
                +icon-mono("tick")(width="11" height="7" class="form__agreement-icon")
                | Я согласен на обработку персональных данных и
                a(href="/")
                  | политикой конфиденциальности
